column5: To my delight, I pulled the tarp off the boat on Thurs and a lovely aroma enticed my senses to throw up.  Looks like the carpets need to be cleaned.  Need to know whats the safe way to wash the carpets down. That will not leave a sent behind.
Take it to the selfserve car wash,and power that puppy with the gun and use the nice smelling pink soap.I did that,and it smells SO NICE.
Don't leave your underwear in the boat next time Paul !
Man yer faster then I Wayne. That was a keeper.L MAO
Don't forget to check the bilge area for rotting bananas!!!!
